nodes.text: The Clan Fishgather was one of the districts of the city of Phemiss, the capital of the planet New Plympto. It was the home of Clan Fishgather, with which the district shared its name, and bordered the Tsilor Sea and four other districts. The district also contained Phemiss' Imperial Consulate. Like the rest of Phemiss, the district's homes were built of adobe.
Clan Flashblade was mentioned in the 2003 Star Wars Roleplaying Game sourcebook Coruscant and the Core Worlds, which was published by Wizards of the Coast.
